docs.text: How to create an enrollment for an existing checklist Requirements Signed Up Logged In One of the following: Imported Checklist Created Checklist Steps Once successfully logged in, click on "Checklists" to access your team's checklists. To access the "Sabbatical Application" checklist, click on its name. To create an enrollment click on "Create Enrollment". To enroll yourself, you must first fill out the "Detail" form, only the Enrollment Name is required. Click "Save" to complete enrollment. To see the newly created enrollment, click on "Enrollments". {.center .small}
